jQuery is a JavaScript Library that is very fast in execution and small in size. 
It simplifies coding by making the codes smaller and easier to write. 
It contains large number of in-built functions that make DOM Manipulations, 
Event Handling, AJAX & API calls, Animation Effects and Validations easier to use. 


Important Features of jQuery

1. Separates JavaScript with HTML
2. Speeds up the Code Development

